      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable daily driver. The exterior shows its age with some visible scratches, minor dings, and slight paint fading on the hood. Inside, the upholstery has noticeable wear and a few stains, though everything remains functional. Mechanically, the car starts and runs well, but the buyer should expect to address some minor suspension noise and upcoming routine maintenance in the near future. It\u2019s a solid, honest car for someone looking for transportation without the premium price tag of a newer model.",
