    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You seriously have to see this absolute beauty in person! I\u2019ve babied this car since day one, and it\u2019s still in truly pristine, showroom condition. It drives like an absolute dream and honestly still has that new-car feel. I\u2019m looking for someone who will love it as much as I have. Feel free to reach out with any questions\u2014I\u2019m super happy to chat and show you around the car!",
      "price": 43500.0,
